{
  "stem": "7093.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Altogether, it was a very, very, very anti-Semitic town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "According to the Jewish Encyclopedia and the Encyclopedia Judaica, it was the most anti-Semitic town in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I only found that out later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Szombathely, yes, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a bishop's seat, a bishopry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was quite a well-known town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in the-- the-- it was actually Sa-- Savaria during the Roman times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And perhaps it's of interest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I was a child, about 11, 11, that's when they discovered that we had two Roman roads and a basilica.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started to do excavations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was incredibly excited about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I used to take all, all visitors, every visitor, very excitedly to show them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, I nearly went there every day, because I was so interested and so excited by it, these excavations.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because it was-- Dan-- Danube-- Pannonia was a Roman province.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Savaria was-- which was Szombathely was before-- I mean, Szombathely-- it became Szombathely-- was the capital of the province.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From some teachers at school, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember having any anti-Semitism from pupils, from co-schoolmates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I actually thought about it very much because four years ago, I was invited to go back to the 50th anniversary of school finishing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I wrote that I think they are mistaken, that I really didn't finish school, they said they knew that, but they still, please, would I come?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they have such nice memories of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would like me to come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And eventually, I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because I started to think that I really didn't have any bad memories regarding my schoolmates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had bad memories from, from teachers, especially my history teacher, which was, again, I mean, it's a different story.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
